          "highlight": [
            "reduced"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "上季他們削減行銷預算後,銷售額大幅下滑。"
          }
        },
        {
          "en": "By reducing waste in the production line, the factory has saved millions.",
          "highlight": [
            "reducing"
          ],
          "translations": {
            "zh-TW": "藉由減少生產線上的浪費,工廠已省下數百萬元。"
          }
        }
